Libptc installation instructions for Linux operation system
===========================================================

1. Install
----------

a. Installation from source package

    Downloaded file is 'libptc-0.4.tar.gz'.

    $ tar -xzf libptc-0.4.tar.gz
    $ cd libptc-0.4
    $ ./configure [--prefix install_path]
    $ make
    # make install

b. Installation from binary package

    Downloaded file is 'libptc-0.4-1.i586.rpm' or
                       'libptc_0.4_i586.deb' or
		       'libptc-0.1-i586-1.tgz'.

    # rpm -ivh libptc-0.4-1.i586.rpm
		or
    # dpkg -i libptc_0.4_i586.deb
		or
    # installpkg libptc-0.1-i586-1.tgz

2. Uninstall
------------

a. Remove with 'make'

    $ cd libptc-0.4
    # make uninstall

b. Remove with package manager

    # rpm -e libptc
	or
    # dpkg -r libptc
	or
    # removepkg libptc

3. Packaging
------------

    # cd libptc-0.4
    # make rpm
	or
    # make deb
	or
    # make tgz

Debian and Slackware package will be in '/usr/src', RPM package will be in 
'/usr/src/RPM/RPMS/ix86' directory.
